description: Already three times this week I saw the same guy in the metro station. As it was always the same time I suppose that he was on his way back home. So this time I was prepared. I switched on my cam and within a few minutes I was already talking to my today´s little toy. Amazingly cute and very well behaved - the young gentleman was willing to talk to me about basically everything. I like this kind of people. He is living in Prague with his girlfriend and he is working as a dancer. This combo turned me on. I was already thinking about how his body was going to look like. Once I got him to a more quiet place the show started. Once again I had to pay more than usual, but only the blow job was worthy enough. So I gather all my courage and asked him the question.
title: Czech Hunter 156
